CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Cuprina Holdings is a Singapore-based biomedical and biotechnology company that is dedicated to the development and commercialization of innovative products for the management of chronic wounds, as well as operating in the health and beauty sectors. Our expertise in biomedical research allows us to identify and utilize materials derived from natural sources to develop wound care products in the form of medical devices which meet international standards. We manufacture and distribute a line of medical grade sterile blowfly larvae bio-dressing products marketed under the MEDIFLY brand name. The MEDIFLY products are used as a biological debridement tool for chronic wounds. In addition to our currently commercialized MEDIFLY products, we have two lines of chronic wound care products in our pipeline.
